Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.79,0:00:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 啊 都說了不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咯吱咯吱咯吱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.07,0:00:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啦 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天女目…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 正好…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是小葉的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.43,0:00:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個掉在泳池旁邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 謝謝 我去拿給她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.52,0:00:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天女目你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.25,0:00:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是渚的姐姐嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都聽到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
